## Subsystems

This harness is a 5-subsystem operating system for AI coding agents
(per *learn-harness-engineering*). Every rule below belongs to
exactly one subsystem; every artifact in this repo serves exactly
one subsystem.

| Subsystem | Minimum artifact | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| **Instructions** | `AGENTS.md` (this file) | Entry, rules, definition of done |
| **State** | `feature_list.json` per spec | Current task, status, evidence |
| **Verification** | `init.sh` + `.harness/scripts/{{ script_shell }}/verify.sh` | Commands the agent MUST run before claiming done |
| **Scope** | `depends_on` graph in `feature_list.json` | Boundaries and what blocks what |
| **Lifecycle** | `specs/<NNN>-<slug>/session-handoff.md` | The next session can resume |

If a new artifact does not map to one of these five, it does not
belong in the harness.

